{{Infobox building |name = Two-storeyed caravanserai |native_name = {{lang-az|İkimərtəbəli karvansaray}} |image = Two floory carvansarai in Baku.JPG |caption = |former_names = |building_type = [[Caravanserai]] |architectural_style = [[Architecture of Azerbaijan|Architectural school of Shirvan-Absheron]] |structural_system = |address = Hagigat Rzayeva Street |location_city = [[File:WP baku siegel.png|22px|]] [[Baku]] |location_country ={{flagicon|Azerbaijan}} [[Azerbaijan]] |location = [[Old City (Baku)|Old City]] |owner = |client = |current_tenants = |landlord = | map_type = Azerbaijan | map_relief = | map_size = | map_caption = Location within Azerbaijan |coordinates = {{coord| 40.365650|N|49.836805|E}} |start_date = |completion_date = XV century |demolition_date = |status = Used as club |material = |height = |diameter = |other_dimensions = |floor_count = |floor_area = |main_contractor = |architect = |structural_engineer = |services_engineer = |civil_engineer = |other_designers = |quantity_surveyor = |awards = }}
'''Two-storeyed''' ({{lang-az|İkimərtəbəli}}) or '''Gasim bey''' caravanserai ({{lang-az|Qasım bəy}}) is a historic monument of the XV century. It is a part of [[Old City (Baku)|Old City]] and located on Hagigat Rzayeva street, in the city of [[Baku]], in [[Azerbaijan]]. The building was also registered as a national architectural monument by the decision of the [[Cabinet of Azerbaijan|Cabinet of Ministers of the Republic of Azerbaijan]] dated August 2, 2001, No. 132.<ref>{{cite web|title=Azərbaycan Respublikası ərazisində dövlət mühafizəsinə götürülmüş daşınmaz tarix və mədəniyyət abidələrinin əhəmiyyət dərəcələrinə görə bölgüsünün təsdiq edilməsi haqqında Azərbaycan Respublikasi Nazirlər Kabinetinin qərarı|url=http://www.e-qanun.az/framework/2847|website=e-qanun.az|accessdate=14 March 2018}}</ref>
==History== The caravanserai was constructed in the XV century. According to the sources, it was built by Shirvan [[Khalilullah I]] and was used by Gasim bey and his followers.<ref name="gomap">{{cite web|title= İkimərtəbəli Kаrvаnsаrаy|url= https://kataloq.gomap.az/az/all-poi/culture/museum/8d4a4e0cd56611e0ad4900226424597d|publisher= kataloq.gomap.az|language= az|accessdate= 14 March 2018}}</ref>
==Architectural features== There are two-sided open entries of the caravanserai placed on the same axis. Entrance to the caravanserai is possible with offshore streets related with sea trade and with a part where trade highway located. It is in square form by its interior structure plan.<ref name="icherisheher"/>
Internal area of the caravanserai is octahedral and it consists of a yard which is surrounded by balconies, where several rooms are located. Covers of rooms and [[dome]]s of balconies are in pointed form. The rooms in the corner are completed with little domes. Entrances to the monument are finished with [[Portal (architecture)|portal]]s bulging at height of the caravanserai and with deep [[niche (architecture)|niche]]s at the level of the first floor. The caravanserai is protected from southeast side with whole corner towers. It also shows its defensive characteristics in the system of city walls.<ref name="icherisheher">{{cite web|title= İkimərtəbəli Kаrvаnsаrаy|url= http://www.icherisheher.gov.az/static,20/lang,az/#monument16|publisher= icherisheher.gov.az|language= az|accessdate= 14 March 2018}}</ref><ref name="gomap"/>
